"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Paradise and Hellfire pray for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever asks Allah for Paradise three times, Paradise will say: O Allah, admit him into Paradise! Whoever seeks protection from Hellfire three times, Hellfire will say: O Allah, save him from the Hellfire!\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39833,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/muadh-final-hadith\/","url_meta":{"origin":37869,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Mu\u2019adh\u2019s final Hadith before he passes away","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: When death was approaching Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal, may Allah be pleased with him, he said, \u201cLift the cloth from my face. I heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say: Whoever testifies that there is no God but Allah, sincerely from his heart, he\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42180,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/08\/23\/allah-is-one-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37869,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: \u2018Allah is One\u2019 leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGive glad tidings to the people that whoever declares there is no God but Allah, he will have Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Nasa\u0304\u2019i\u0304 10885 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20473,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/16\/khatam-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37869,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Last deeds are righteous, enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever declares there is no God but Allah, seeking the countenance of Allah as his last deed, he will enter Paradise. Whoever fasts a day, seeking the countenance of Allah as his last deed, he will enter Paradise. Whoever\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42174,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/08\/23\/take-not-for-granted\/","url_meta":{"origin":37869,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Take not Allah\u2019s promise for granted","author":"Abu Amina El